## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources and the scope of the search. The definitions and characteristics of society can vary significantly across different cultures and academic disciplines, which may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may introduce biases based on the accessibility and popularity of certain viewpoints. Further research could include more academic and peer-reviewed sources to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.